STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Sean C. COGDELL, a/k/a Sean Gogdell, Sean Gogdett, Dwight S. Murphy, Sean C. Cogdell Ivy Dante and Ivy Donte, Defendant-Petitioner. C-537 September Term 2017
079879 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 2, 2018 **144To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005486-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

**145It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
